-- Shares in Banca Carige suspended from trading after 8 pct drop
-- By Francesca Landini
-- Fri Oct 31, 2014 05:21AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, Oct 31 (Reuters) - Shares in Banca Carige were suspended from trading on Friday after an 8 percent drop as investors worried about the ability of the Italian lender to fill a capital hole unveiled by a Europe-wide health check on banks.

